name: FRINGE VIDEO SHOP COLLECTIVE PACK / MOVIE EDITION

metadata.name: Collective Pack Gen0 #1
metadata.description:
In the FRINGE VIDEO SHOP, there is a vending machine where you can purchase goods designed related to the MOVIE EDITION. These goods are called COLLECTIVE PACKs and are released in limited quantities each time a new MOVIE EDITION is announced. You do not know what you will get until you purchase, but the rarity is divided according to the design, and attractive benefits are granted according to the rarity.
At the time of purchase, the pack is in a state of pack, but when you enter the wallet and press the Refresh Metadata button, the design will change according to the rarity of the pack.
